display="inline"><![CDATA[S\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> is defined to be the <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00LO.xml"
addr="jms-00LO"
title="Predicate">predicate</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _S\colon  A\to  {\mathopen {}\left  [2\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> defined piecewise below:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \chi _S{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}} = \begin {cases}   1 & \text {if } a \in  S\\   0 & \text {if } a \not \in  S  \end {cases} ]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
